quotas.name: HP State Quota
quotas.tooltip_content:
**Eligibility for the Quota : HP State Quota**
1. Bonafide Himachali Students (or) 
2. Children of Bonafide Himachali, wherever schooling is
3. If not a bonafide as above then the Children who studied XI and XII in any board in HP AND their parents have worked for two years in the last 4 years on or before Jan 1st of the year of passing XII exam AND fall of any one of the below    
a. Working in Central Govt / AIS / Central Civil Services   
b. Employees working in Autonomous bodies/ Institutes/Orgns/SemiGovt    
c. Serving Judges of HP High court  
d. Regular employees of HP Govt or Govt undertakings  / autonomous bodies wholly owned by HP govt (however for this category d) schooling condition is not there (XI and XII need not be in HP) if their parents are posted outisde Himachal for at least 3 continuous years as on Jan 1st of the year of passing XII examinations)
